VideoArch team is a middle platform team which provides SDK and backend services for ByteDance's top apps like Tiktok, and also delivers toB products such as VideoCloud, focusing on Live-Streaming. VideoArch QA team provides solid quality support for these businesses with good deliveries. VideoArch QA team consists of client-side QA sub-team, service-side QA sub-team and business technical support sub-team.

Responsibilities
1. Taking ownership of product quality on live-streaming from the service-side including designing test plan, writing test cases, executing functional/performance tests, verifying bug fixes and giving test reports;
2. Responsible for tracking task progress, assessing potential risk, coordinating across teams, providing delivery with good quality;
3. Responsible for developing automation new features and regression test cases and building CICD related work;
4. Responsible for building/optimizing development and QA process to help improve quality and efficiency. 

Qualifications

 1. Bachelor's degree in Information Technology, Computer Science or relevant;
2. Proven work experience in QA, functional and performance testing, experience in service side testing is a plus;
3. Demonstrated coding skills in python/go/java, experience on automation test framework like pytest/testNG is a plus;
4. Excellent learning, troubleshooting, and communication skills;
5. Passionate, self-motivated and good teamwork skills.

